					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9842883#post-4109682</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9842883/scp-4450#post-4109682</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 Jan 2019 21:34:36 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Gabriel Jade</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>414239</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Answers&nbsp;&amp;&nbsp;spoilers&nbsp;within</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>1: Rhi-0 was offered a deal they couldn't refuse.</p> <p>2: The method of changing the code isn't stated, but each previous owner, eg. Serpent's Hand and Chicago Spirit were able to alter the code during the 1930's when no computers existed.</p> <p>3: The door is shut and locked from the inside. They merely affixed their explosives to the outside of the locked door.</p> <p>4: They don't care <em>who</em> incurred the debt specifically; it was done and the Debtors are out to collect funds for repayment, they don't particularly care from whom.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9842883#post-4109666</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9842883/scp-4450#post-4109666</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 Jan 2019 21:17:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Drblackbox</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2785951</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">So,&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;a&nbsp;little&nbsp;confused.&nbsp;(spoilers)</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Title&nbsp;for&nbsp;hiding&nbsp;text</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Did Rhi-0 become the new SCP-4450? If so, why? I was under the impression the old SCP-4450 instances &quot;made a deal&quot; to get their abilities and tied in with the debt.</p> <p>When did Rhi-0 learn to edit the code? *How* did they edit the code? Does the casino have a computer to put in a new password with somewhere?</p> <p>How did the GOC access the door to test all the stuff?</p> <p>Why is the Foundation indebted? Did they somehow indirectly cause the damages?</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
