					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9842883#post-4109604</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9842883/scp-4450#post-4109604</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 05 Jan 2019 19:57:18 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ayers</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1856789</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NCkwAgTcDBw">Getting to it? That's not the hard part.</a></p> <div style="text-align: right;"> <p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NCkwAgTcDBw">... It's letting go.</a></p> </div> <hr /> <p>This is a COLLABORATION between <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546720321" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span> and myself, and our entry into Clichecon! Which cliches did we choose? Well&#8230; all of them. If we have to boil it down to two, though:</p> <ul> <li>A doorway (of any shape) to another dimension/timeline/world</li> <li>(GOI/POI) gets one over the Foundation, making them look like fools in the process.</li> </ul> <p>This was an absolute blast to write, and even more fun to brainstorm.</p> <p><sub>also we got HTML to work with listpages somehow, which was nice.</sub></p> <hr /> <p>Crit Credits:<br /> Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/geckoguy2704" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2923244&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546720321" alt="Geckoguy2704" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2923244)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/geckoguy2704" >Geckoguy2704</a></span>, Reedming Qual may not Apply (from discord), <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546720321" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" >not_a_seagull</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546720321" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kindlyturtlerock" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4504036&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546720321" alt=" KindlyTurtleRock" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4504036)" /></a> <a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kindlyturtlerock" >KindlyTurtleRock</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546720321" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span> for feedback!</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Image&nbsp;Credits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7d/Casino_Ballroom%2C_MON_1909.jpg/800px-Casino_Ballroom%2C_MON_1909.jpg">https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/7d/Casino_Ballroom%2C_MON_1909.jpg/800px-Casino_Ballroom%2C_MON_1909.jpg</a><br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:StateLibQ